<plot>Martin Gimbley is a man with nothing left to lose. Facing life in prison for his crimes he decides to make a deal that will allow him to escape his fate. However, Martin soon learns that things can always get worse, and when you make a deal with the Devil himself there is no backing out. This short proves that seven minutes is an eternity when you're facing your own private Hell.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?359406</url></doc>
